                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-ide-prt              .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Messaggio                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "WR"                 to   m-ope                  .
           move      spaces               to   m-msg                  .
           string    "Archivio ["
                                delimited by   size
                     f-xxx-nam  delimited by   spaces
                     "] ID "    delimited by   size
                     w-ide-dat  delimited by   spaces
                     " - "      delimited by   size
